# Header

Site-wide header rendered at the top of every page by `BaseLayout`. Ported from the Hugo `main-nav` partial — dimensions, colors, shadows, breakpoints, hover timings, and interactions all match the Hugo site. The header you see above this content is the component itself.

## Sub-components

| Component | Type | Role |
|-----------|------|------|
| `Header.astro` | Astro (static) | Nav shell — reads menu data at build time and renders logo, left menu, right menu, and hamburger statically for SEO. |
| `NavDropdown.tsx` | Preact island | Hover-open dropdown used for Solutions, About, and Blog menus. Opens on mouse-enter, closes 150ms after mouse-leave. |
| `ProductMegaMenu.tsx` | Preact island | The Product dropdown. Holds `openCategory` state with a 160ms hover debounce; resets to the first category when the dropdown closes. |
| `LogoDownloadPanel.astro` | Static + tiny `<script is:inline>` | Hidden "Looking for Datadog logos?" popover. Click-toggle behavior mirrors Hugo's `.js-logo-download`. |
| `HeaderScroll.astro` | `<script is:inline>` | Adds `.main-nav-scrolled` to `<html>` once `scrollY > 30` at ≥992px (matching Hugo's `tailwind-main-nav.html`). The class snaps the nav from 130→65px, animates the bits logo 75→50px, and hides the wordmark — all via a shared 200ms ease-in-out transition. |
| `MobileNav.tsx` | Preact island | Hamburger-triggered right-side overlay. Renders the docs mobile nav variant with home/docs/api quick-links, search stub, and full menu tree. Receives already-resolved labels and URLs as props so the client bundle doesn't pull in `menuData` / `i18n` / `yaml`. |
| `NavIcon.astro` | Static | Renders a websites-modules iconfont icon (`<i class="icon-{name}">`) and colors it via `currentColor`. |

## Data flow

Menu data is loaded at build time via `src/lib/menuData.ts`, which reads `data/menu_data/*.yaml` directly from `@websites-modules`. Labels go through the `i18n(key)` helper in `src/lib/i18n.ts`, which reads `i18n/*.yaml` from `@websites-modules`. URLs are normalized with `resolveUrl()` so relative paths become `https://www.datadoghq.com/…`.

## Dimensions (Hugo-identical)

| Viewport | Header height | Behavior on scroll |
|----------|---------------|--------------------|
| <992px   | 60px          | No change |
| ≥992px, `scrollY ≤ 30` | 130px | Resting state. |
| ≥992px, `scrollY > 30` | 65px  | `.main-nav-scrolled` is added: the nav, bits logo, and wordmark all transition together over 200ms ease-in-out. |

The corresponding tokens live in the Hugo-identical section of `src/styles/tokens.css`.
